{"word":"G1287 - διασκορπίζω - diaskorpízō - dee-as-kor-pid'-zo - Disperse","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διασκορπίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diaskorpízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-as-kor-pid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Disperse</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தெளி, சிதறடி, அழி"},{"paragraph":"to scatter abroad, disperse"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G4650 - σκορπίζω - skorpízō - skor-pid'-zo/4650\">G4650</a>; to <i>dissipate</i>, that is, (generally) to <i>rout</i> or <i>separate</i>; specifically to <i>winnow</i>; figuratively to <i>squander:</i> - disperse, scatter (abroad), strew, waste.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1287/1287\">G1287</a>, <a href=\"#/G4650/4650\">G4650</a>"}]}